      behavior of circuit elements like resistors, capacitors, and inductors.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>
      This subject forms the foundation of electrical and electronics engineering.
      It explains how electrical energy is generated, transmitted, and consumed.
    </p>
